702019f-a.title: Bronx: Washington Avenue - 3rd Avenue
702019f-a.text:
The intersection of Washington Avenue (right) and Third Avenue,
looking northward. The triangular area, in the foreground, is a
public park.
May 4, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
